description: In this video, I show you how to make tofu scramble! In my cookbook, I have a recipe for my dreamy tofu scramble recipe which is more similar to tofu scrambled eggs. In the vegan breakfast recipe I'm sharing today I amp it up by packing in the veggies to make it the best vegan tofu scramble for a hearty and satisfying start to your day. Wonderful paired with avocado slices and toast.
name: How To Make Tofu Scramble - Vegan Breakfast Recipe Easy
